.TH "ufshcd_query_flag" 9 "ufshcd_query_flag" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ufshcd_query_flag \- API function for sending flag query requests
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ufshcd_query_flag
.BI "(struct ufs_hba *hba "  ","
.BI "enum query_opcode opcode "  ","
.BI "enum flag_idn idn "  ","
.BI "u8 index "  ","
.BI "bool *flag_res "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hba" 12
per-adapter instance
.IP "opcode" 12
flag query to perform
.IP "idn" 12
flag idn to access
.IP "index" 12
flag index to access
.IP "flag_res" 12
the flag value after the query request completes
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 0 for success, non-zero in case of failure
